{"tid":1628810,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［澄清］百萬大遊行唔代表一區遊行","createTime":"2019-10-06T04:46:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T05:07:58.000Z","uid":152018,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"493863bed74e9bb045ab4251a8c0fd11eaa2571c","tid":1628810,"uid":152018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:46:17.000Z","msg":"[size=4]如果仲堅持要港島集合、又話九龍條遊行路線好危險既人唔該你諗清楚。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>港島次次無車比人走你唔講？<br />\n<br />\n次次行過狗總政總你唔話好危險？<br />\n<br />\n彌敦道成條大直路佈滿人畫面又唔好睇？</strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">百萬大遊行唔係代表要港島集合，麻煩諗清楚。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">今日和理非目標好清晰，2區遊行</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FC3uGat.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFC3uGat.jpg&h=1f24f9eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">勇武小心行事，自己做野，18區任你發揮！<br />\n你地反而先係唔需要比幾多區綁手綁腳既人！</span>"},{"pid":"bab4e55b55768b9257de1cdd0de4fdd337e6146e","tid":1628810,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:47:39.000Z","msg":"【國際線行動】應盡快整理612後警暴片段，同納粹暴行做對比，爭取西方實際行動支持香港<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1628720\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1628720</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請幫手推文支持<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1628720\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1628720</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"fe51eefe8c9e6044ffb9a4640ffda43ac97c3f6d","tid":1628810,"uid":152018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:49:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">話唔圍深水埗，九龍區終點可改用九龍塘</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WyGssSC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWyGssSC.jpg&h=f8914f42&